---
import BaseHead from "../components/BaseHead.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import { SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from "../consts";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      .now-page {
        font-style: italic;
        font-size: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Now</h1>
      <h3>What i'm working on</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Renovation work in all my house</li>
        <li>Building this blog</li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/ChuckBDT/reparo" target="_blank">Reparo</a
          > : a computer repair shop management software.
        </li>
        <li>
          Learning properly PostgreSQL with courses and documentation. I was
          more a MongoDB user until now.
        </li>
        <li>
          My Unraid server : just installed <a
            href="https://immich.app/"
            target="_blank">Immich</a
          > which is awesome (open source replacement for Apple/Google photos), i
          might buy a new CPU soon because my i3 6100 is a bit outdated.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3>What i'm reading</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Les_Carnets_du_sous-sol"
            target="_blank">Les Carnets du sous-sol</a
          > by Dostoïveski
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.babelio.com/livres/Mhalla-Cyberpunk--Le-nouveau-systeme-totalitaire/1922751"
            target="_blank">Cyberpunk : Le nouveau système totalitaire</a
          > by Asma Mhalla
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ravage_(roman)" target="_blank"
            >Ravage</a
          > by René Barjavel
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h3>What i'm watching</h3>
      <h4>Movies</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kaamelott_:_Deuxi%C3%A8me_Volet,_partie_1"
            target="_blank">Kaamelott : Deuxième Volet, partie 1</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h4>TV shows</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Person_of_Interest"
            target="_blank">Person of Interest</a
          >: I randomly discovered it and it's good, interesting enough to be
          watched and not too brain burning. I like to watch an episode from
          time to time before bed.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <h4>YouTube</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Casey" target="_blank"
            >Casey Neistat</a
          >: It's been years i haven't watched his videos but YT recommended me
          his channel recently. I forgot how much i enjoyed his videos back in
          the days. I'm curious to know what he's up to now.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="now-page">
        <b>Last updated on 28/02/2026</b><br />
        This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank">/now</a> page.
        If you have your own site, you should make one too.
      </p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
